testcase.name: ActivationResponse should interpret failed init that does not response

ActivationResponse should interpret failed init that responds with empty string
ActivationResponse should interpret failed init that responds with non-empty string
ActivationResponse should interpret failed init that responds with JSON string not object
ActivationResponse should interpret failed init that responds with JSON object containing error
ActivationResponse should interpret failed init that responds with JSON object
ActivationResponse should not interpret successful init
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that does not response
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that responds with null string
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that responds with empty string
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that responds with non-empty string
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that responds with JSON string not object
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that responds with JSON object containing error
ActivationResponse should interpret failed run that responds with JSON object
ActivationResponse should interpret successful run that responds with JSON object containing error
ActivationResponse should interpret successful run that responds with JSON object
